      "date": "2018-10-25 00:18:36.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1: Verified+1\n\nPassed enforced test review-ldiskfs on CentOS 7.0/x86_64 uploaded by Onyx Autotest from onyx-30vm1: https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/19c4e535-9358-4c60-88fe-4d0e85151553 ran 4 tests.",
