        "_account_id": 117,
        "name": "Andreas Dilger",
        "email": "adilger@thelustrecollective.com",
        "username": "adilger"
      },
      "date": "2018-10-25 04:50:31.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nI'm happy to see additional reviewers.  I haven't yet worked out how get_maintainers.pl will be used to automatically add reviewers to a patch.\n\nOne option (which is easiest to implement), would be to add CC: lines to the commit message, but this does not automatically trigger reviewers to be added to the patch in Gerrit.\n\nAnother option is to have the WC Checkpatch script add the reviewers to the patch when it reviews the code style.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 1
    },
